vclaim: Keanu Reeves gave an envelope of cash to a stranger in order to help pay for a kidney transplant.
title: Did Keanu Reeves Help Pay for a Stranger’s Kidney Transplant with an Envelope of Cash?
subtitle: Two unrelated photographs were circulated on social media along with a story about actor Keanu Reeves' paying for stranger's kidney transplant.
author: Dan Evon
